Author: paperklipp
Text: In my experience, the only people who get it are people who have it too. That’s why this sub is such a revelation, you see people posting “DAE...?” and you’re like “Holy shit? Yes???”   It’s dangerous though because it’s in the disorder’s nature to compete with itself. So you get too close to other sufferers and suddenly you’re in competition with them. It’s very push-and-pull.
